elements.name: View a subscription via admin panel

steps.name: a registered user with an active subscription
an admin user with access to their info
the admin user visits the admin page
logs in as an admin
views the subscription's information
the subscription information should be displayed

elements.name: Mark a subscription as having an invalid address

steps.name: a registered user with an active subscription
an admin user with access to their info
the admin user visits the admin page
logs in as an admin
flags the subscription as having an invalid address
the subscription should have a status of ACTIVE / HOLD in the admin panel

elements.name: Netherlands user signs up for random month subscription

steps.name: a registered user with a Netherlands address
the user logs in
the user selects the Loot Crate crate
the user sets their country to Netherlands
the user selects a random month subscription plan
the user submits valid subscription information
the new subscription should be added to the user account
recurly should have a matching international subscription
the recurly billing address should have no state
the user should receive a subscription confirmation email
